p: Filed on the 21st day of Oct 1887

I hereby certify that the within recognizance was entered just before in and acknowledged before me and the same is hereby certified to the Clerk of the District Clerk for paged in accordance with the provisions of Section 1035 of the Code of Washington Territory.
Witnessed my hand this 20th day of October 1887
W.H. Bush Sheriff of Chehalis County
